Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道是喜歡還是討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想打炮罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本不是更加讓人開心幸福的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會讓人這麼辛苦疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛什麼的 我真的不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你現在深陷其中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00E1B80F&}怎麼這樣！在大家的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒說討厭你嘛…秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然豁出去表了白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 就是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差你沒投票了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投啥票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的人氣投票啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上男生偷偷進行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女生保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都聽到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 事實么現在是山田和金城單挑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也選一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 這是無記名投票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提 現在她們並列第一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一票 決定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我投誰不就馬上知道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城跟山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我選的話 自然是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我這種人選了 山田只會覺得討厭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快投我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在期待我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怏決定啊 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我選了山田 金城肯定會覺得不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 金城對這種無聊的事應該不會感興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是啥 幻覺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慢吞吞的 不像爺們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個爺們...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 平常的我都不像個爺們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山 山 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡山田啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:04:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 人氣投票 你搞什麼愛的告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 好大膽 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音真大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投票進箱不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底笨到什麼地步啊 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過...呼吸好困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚快要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼胸口好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道...這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是被他表白嘛 我怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區小須田 區區小須田 區區小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很難做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會了還壯烈犧牲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠爺們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上 不就是個人氣投票嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 小須田的表情 是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那表情也很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田那傢伙 真是個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏今天情緒那麼高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為那樣我會高興嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為我會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 剩下的只要直奔床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了 這次真的傳達給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小山田同不同意又是另一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你是我的敵人？ 夥伴？ 還是貪好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城 ~ 連著去年的選美 這次又輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 你又讓我蒙羞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 紅茶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 市原小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等著瞧 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 忘記拿砂糖給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用錯表情了哦 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田 昨天真帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然公開表白 有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下美好回憶了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經成回憶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥不給他個答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田都鼓起勇氣表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本他是那麼靦腆 膽怯 優柔寡斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不用說到那份上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也多考慮一下小須田的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想想他是懷著什麼樣的覺悟來表白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時也是 他是什麼樣的心情...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我腦裡只想著打炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早就知道了 你這麼一說 小須田超可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你也說喜歡他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是為了打炮 我也不能說謊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 那不是謊言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也為之前躲著他道個歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 說句看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這態度 算是道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要道歉 也沒有跟他單獨在一起的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到體育祭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命去爭取吧 就算吐血也要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是體育老師說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢 我們來選體育祭的執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人毛遂自薦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定沒人舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田跟山田 你們這對告白情侶來當好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 你這是性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 連老師都知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼尷尬的狀況 山田怎麼可能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 沒辦法了呢 我就當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我略帶羨慕地逗逗你們罷了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育祭的競技項目就跟往年一樣就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒人有新奇的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女混合組合體操
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女混合二人三足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 情緒很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們選個記錄員吧 就是負責拍照的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料室有去年及以前的照片 可以參考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料室...在哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很熟悉的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料室原來是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻站著幹嘛 資料在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速發展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窄小的密室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你先請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...前段時間 我都躲著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難開口 不過一定要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她說「以後你多躲著我」的話 就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟你道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了 說不出第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個...我完全沒放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說謊的 其實很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超鬱悶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 上次人氣投票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那表白 我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以的話 能不能給個答覆...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底遲鈍到什麼地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想想我是為了什麼才道的歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她生氣了？ 還是很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的話 就直說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會乾脆放棄的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哭的話 就別說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒說...討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭...我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定...我可以期待一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你這木頭人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭他...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經跟OK一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說討厭的話 就打不成炮了 只是這樣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥總是想撮合我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你自己也察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實認了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是喜歡小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會受打擊 就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣 太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛什麼的 原本不是更加讓人開心幸福的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你現在深陷其中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎再次乘坐我們的航班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟各位美女一起度過空中時間 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藝人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不行的話 至少請告訴我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這次微服出訪結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說「讓我最開心的地方是成田」的 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫 金城圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫 金城圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫 金城圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00E1B80F&}賭上體育祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛咋咋…秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動的青春 體育祭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 何等盛況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年H班 聲援對戰上要當啦啦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 性感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我不是故意的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了 真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你的器量就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好不容易能見到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會在意山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 過後說不定要報復 先記上好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼慌張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不想見到小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都不知道用什麼表情見他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是照樣擺Pose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田好像還在躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松尾哥 好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 跟你說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也挺在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會覺得煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 對山田來說 他完全是個外人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這種事 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 小須田 我全聽美春說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 據你說來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田應該也很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對方不在她心上 就不會做出這麼多事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你可以稍稍放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我經常會想「這其實是夢吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愛瞎操心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想一直躲著小須田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決不了任何問題哦 你想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田光躺著不吭聲 我來主導
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你光躺著不吭聲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十個 甚至上百個小須田都能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 浪費 太浪費這美貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城 你真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服 很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城 你有沒有男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對哥哥一條心 不需要什麼男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 說沒有的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了那麼多狂言 竟然沒個男朋友 笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個超級帥哥男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣嗎 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼窩心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道山田 你沒有男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我說中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 金城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 有 還是沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接不來是二年級女生的騎馬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才她「切」了一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個項目 二年級女生的騎馬戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城知道我沒男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為比賽到最後你還能留著頭帶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你們是一夥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對滅了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去金城那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪就交給當腳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳只是裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聽騎手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別脫掉頭帶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美春？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真不怕人見到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣你才沒男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得這麼漂亮 真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是擔心自己好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那男朋友 看我把他搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你敢對哥哥出手 我索性...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才 想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 山田你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿姐姐沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰 超帥的 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京香？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鄉 到你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上 什麼都能借到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是帥哥的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過後要還人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有「帥哥」之類的選項
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鄉之眼 發動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:17:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 「帥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的透視毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥哥 帥哥在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 京香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的 要讓人家等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉京香 我現在有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥哥 帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥哥 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個帥哥是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你 能告訴我們名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是2年H班 金城京香的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥哥 帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 京香 很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎馬戰跟京香對抗的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是金城圭一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帥哥是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼輕快地說山田漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他帶的那部相機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高端的數碼單反機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他的一比 我手上這台...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二手的膠片機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是規格上差異
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說次元不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本戰不過他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在久違的日本 竟然能遇到你這等美女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為親近的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田股價急升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 竟然讓哥哥丟臉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能輕易到手的話 就無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個怎樣的女孩？ 京香的對手麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 他很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處躲著他 真累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 該用什麼表情對他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...剛才金城的哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對金城哥哥那麼冷淡 是為了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想得太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才 才沒有 誰會為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不問 我也不能這樣回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 金城的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哥哥...兩 兩兄妹都很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥要生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒誇過我漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要稱讚一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛啊 性感啊 萌啊之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田的啦啦隊打扮 超可愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還早了百萬年！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人太囧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 那個 下次能不能跟我去個什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿誠意的約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要搞定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繃緊心情其他地方攻陷他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班女生的級數真高
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養眼啊 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 你跑去哪了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上 2年H班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...我想更加瞭解山田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小須田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大殺必死
